<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<!-- saved from url=(0014)about:internet -->

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <meta name="keywords" content="磷酸锰铁锂,LMFP,NMC+LMFP二代磷酸铁锂,电池材料,软包电池,高电压,高电压三元,高导电设计,高离子,高品质稳定奈米材料,自制奈米化设备,泓辰量产技术,泓辰电池材料,适用於车用电池,适用於大巴电池">
